# Changelog

## [1.0] - 2026-03-07
### Added
- Initial project files
- Medic logic and elevate Recorder hook thread identity
    - Recorder will now correctly log every ability (Medic, Mercenary base, DJ etc...)
- Trial elevator teleport
    - Library will now teleport to the Trial elevator when calling TDS:Mode("Trial") function

### Fixed
- UnlockSpeedTickets crash when the TimeScale UI option is pre-enabled
	- TDS:UnlockTimeScale() will no longer cause an error if Timescale is pre-enabled in the UI

### Changed
- Updated loadstrings to local repo